title: Multilingual Poetry Collection 001
creator: Various
description:
The First LibriVox Multilingual Poetry Collection, where LibriVox volunteers read their favourite public-domain poems in languages other than English.
The LibriVox catalog page for this work lists the authors and the LibriVox readers, and has links to the texts. For more information on LibriVox, or to volunteer, please see:http://librivox.org/ M4B Audiobook (18MB)
source: Librivox recording of a public-domain text
